    "List of AUX devices that should NOT be displayed. This field requires a regular expression and cannot be left empty. If you do not want to filter any devices, you must provide a regex that matches none of the entries.\n\nExamples:\n\nNo entries: /^none$/\nFilter out 'Ground Floor': /^Ground Floor$/\nFilter out 'Ground Floor' and 'First Floor': /^Ground Floor$|^First Floor$/\nFilter out everything starting with 'Distributor': /^Distributor.*$/": "不应显示的 AUX 设备列表。此字段需要正则表达式，且不能为空。如果不想过滤任何设备，必须提供一个与所有条目都不匹配的 regex。\n\n示例：\n\n无条目： /^none$/\n过滤 'Ground Floor'： /^Ground Floor$/\n过滤 'Ground Floor' 和 'First Floor'： /^Ground Floor$|^First Floor$/\n过滤所有以 'Distributor' 开头的内容： /^Distributor.*$/",
    "List of EXT devices that should NOT be displayed. This field requires a regular expression and cannot be left empty. If you do not want to filter any devices, you must provide a regex that matches none of the entries.\n\nExamples:\n\nNo entries: /^none$/\nFilter out 'Ground Floor': /^Ground Floor$/\nFilter out 'Ground Floor' and 'First Floor': /^Ground Floor$|^First Floor$/\nFilter out everything starting with 'Distributor': /^Distributor.*$/": "不应显示的 EXT 设备列表。此字段需要正则表达式，且不能为空。如果不想过滤任何设备，必须提供一个与所有条目都不匹配的 regex。\n\n示例：\n\n无条目： /^none$/\n过滤 'Ground Floor'： /^Ground Floor$/\n过滤 'Ground Floor' 和 'First Floor'： /^Ground Floor$|^First Floor$/\n过滤所有以 'Distributor' 开头的内容： /^Distributor.*$/",
    "List of loadpoints that should NOT be displayed. The expression is a regular expression that must start and end with /. It must not be empty; if nothing should be filtered, provide a regular expression that matches none of the entries.\n\nExamples:\nNo entries: /^none$/\nFilter out 'Garage': /^Garage$/\nFilter out 'Garage' and 'Parking Spot': /^Garage$|^Parking Spot$/\nFilter out everything that starts with 'foo': /^foo.*$/": "List of loadpoints that should NOT be displayed. The expression is a regular expression that must start and end with /. It must not be empty; if nothing should be filtered, provide a regular expression that matches none of the entries.\n\nExamples:\nNo entries: /^none$/\nFilter out 'Garage': /^Garage$/\nFilter out 'Garage' and 'Parking Spot': /^Garage$|^Parking Spot$/\nFilter out everything that starts with 'foo': /^foo.*$/",
    "List of loadpoints that should NOT be displayed. This field requires a regular expression and cannot be left empty. If you do not want to filter any entries, you must provide a regex that does not match any existing loadpoint.\n\nExamples:\n\nNo entries: ^none$\nFilter out 'Garage': ^Garage$\nFilter out 'Garage' and 'Parking Spot': ^Garage$|^Parking Spot$\nFilter out everything starting with 'foo': ^foo.*$": "不应显示的充电点列表。此字段需要正则表达式，且不能为空。如果不想过滤任何条目，必须提供一个与现有充电点都不匹配的 regex。\n\n示例：\n\n无条目： ^none$\n过滤 'Garage'： ^Garage$\n过滤 'Garage' 和 'Parking Spot'： ^Garage$|^Parking Spot$\n过滤所有以 'foo' 开头的内容： ^foo.*$",
    "List of vehicles that should NOT be displayed. This field must contain a regular expression and cannot be left empty. If you do not want to filter any vehicles, you must provide a regex that matches none of the entries.\n\nExamples:\n\nNo entries: ^none$\nFilter out 'Garage': ^Garage$\nFilter out 'Garage' and 'Parking Spot': ^Garage$|^Parking Spot$\nFilter out vehicles ending with '(offline)': ^.*\\(offline\\)$": "不应显示的车辆列表。此字段必须包含正则表达式，且不能为空。如果不想过滤任何车辆，必须提供一个与所有条目都不匹配的 regex。\n\n示例：\n\n无条目： ^none$\n过滤 'Garage'： ^Garage$\n过滤 'Garage' 和 'Parking Spot'： ^Garage$|^Parking Spot$\n过滤所有以 '(offline)' 结尾的车辆： ^.*\\(offline\\)$",
